Steps to Run the grow_replicas script:-

1)  First  Run the setup.sh script

	Usage to run setup.sh is

	$ ./setup.sh  $diskname1  $diskname2
	
	( eg . $] ./setup.sh  sda sdc )


2) Second run the grow_replicas_001_pos.ksh  script

	$  ./grow_replicas_001_pos.ksh    $additional_disk1  $additional_disk2 

	( eg . $] ./grow_pool_001_pos.ksh sdd sde)

3) Lastly run the cleanup.sh  script

	$ ./cleanup.sh 


